## Branches

### main
- Default branch.
- Commit directly.
- Tag semantic versions when stable.

### feature/*
- Branch from main when work spans > one session.
- Merge back with fast-forward (`--no-ff`) if you need a merge commit marker.
- Delete after merge.

### hotfix/*
- Branch from tagged commit when a production patch is needed.
- Merge back into main, retag.

## Commit messages
Format: `type: short statement`
Types: feat, fix, docs, refactor, test, chore.

## Pull requests
Optional. Use only when CI or code-review tooling adds value.

## Protection
Enable only if you add automated tests or deployment hooks.